e47faeb","tid":1174822,"uid":65686,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又諗起嗰句說話「<span style=\"color: red;\">我們</span>要不惜一切<span style=\"color: red;\">代價</span>去打貿易戰，我以為我係我們的一份子，點知原來我只不過係代價」"},{"pid":"76f11d00ad794b601ec78c33c1ed0549352c1d24","tid":1174822,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"支持強囯繼續放水<br />\n物價炒上天"},{"pid":"389b1c411a3031dfcd48b09a2839e315d69a1013","tid":1174822,"uid":41545,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"50蚊人仔一個蘋果既時代都未來臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n米酒鹽都十倍增幅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bd537e87db1c3d37cb38cf28a2ebf5e4309e7c","tid":1174822,"uid":12609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:14:03.000Z","msg":"今次真係滯漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那仆街了"},{"pid":"45610bdbb57d9481d6b28efacc53b2ef2f496362","tid":1174822,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:14:33.000Z","msg":"爆啦爆啦<br />\n終於去到銀紙唔值錢了"},{"pid":"ba56cc1261db00d59b3604d1df3ac0a786b38dbf","tid":1174822,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:14:55.000Z","msg":"質班撚樣食草就岩<br />\n<br />\n繼續升番幾倍物價就好了"},{"pid":"0d5e20fd387b350e79f314601dac08da3a36597d","tid":1174822,"uid":174767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba56cc1261db00d59b3604d1df3ac0a786b38dbf","tid":1174822,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:14:55.000Z","msg":"質班撚樣食草就岩<br />\n<br />\n繼續升番幾倍物價就好了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:16:06.000Z","msg":"草? $40 斤，想要幾多？"},{"pid":"0477185003b61453a8d106ff8